description: For sale: $779,900. Welcome home to 465 Westover Rd.  This immaculate custom designed log home has 5 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms and a two car matching log garage with an apartment/studio above (partially finished), is located on a beautiful 10 acre lot.  The home is conveniently located just minutes away from State Highway 61. It was designed to be environmentally friendly and efficient, utilizing in-floor geothermal heating, on demand water heater, energy efficient windows, and low VOC paints/stains. You will really enjoy the ice cold artesian well water. The open floor plan is very welcoming and great for entertaining.  Natural luxury is evident throughout with cork, hardwood, porcelain, and slate floorings, Tiffany inspired light fixtures, marble, onyx, and copper bowls, 3 master baths, solid Scandinavian wood doors, a kitchen with Jurassic black granite counters and island, and hickory cabinets.  The lower level is a walkout basement with a fully equipped kitchenette with two bedrooms and a bathroom suitable for guest quarters or a family game room and office space. Besides all this, there are apple trees, a grape arbor, raspberry bushes, aronia berries, Russian black currants, an acre pasture, and a large organic garden. The home is equipped with fiber optic high-speed broadband internet. With so much to offer, be sure to check out this home.

description: For sale: $169,900. I have been maintained very well, my owner loves me and how close I am to Lake Superior, Castle Danger Brewery, restaurants, parks and paved walking trails, she smiles every time she comes home. I have beautiful hardwood floors, a stunning wood banister and the sun porch holds a special place in her heart, it keeps her so warm even in the depths of a Minnesota winter.  I am excited to have new owners love me and take care of me like she has!  Looking forward to meeting you!  -The House * We are not allowing showings at this time.

description: Recently sold: $350,000. Location, Location! Absolutely gorgeous 4 BR, 4BA with lake view on 11 acres next to city limits. Top quality construction throughout (Harju Construction) with plastered walls and cast iron baseboard heating on main level. Master suite with bath and 3 additional bedrooms and bath on upper level. The main level features an oak eat-in kitchen with built-ins and granite countertops, a formal dining room with Brazilian cherry floors open to the formal living room. The main floor family room features a wood-burning heat circulating fireplace and main floor laundry and powder room complete the main level amenities.
